{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 MIDI Transposer.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Map each note played to a new scale. Root & scale must be provided for both the 'from' scale and the 'to' scale.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Scales are defined as Reaper scale .txt files, and should be in the ix_scales folder. This script assumes one scale per file.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
