{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Will add sin curve modulation per note based on input info... Not all voices do that, so adds a little character to dull tones... This particular script works on all selected takes/tracks. Not required to be working within the MIDI Editor, but your MIDI notes need to be selected.\par}
